des:
Get unofficial to-the-minute stats & fun facts on the Titans by Fresh Digital Group. This skill isn’t sponsored or endorsed by the Titans.

Here’s some ways you can use the skill. We have given you many different ways for you to talk to Alexa:



General Updates:


Alexa, ask Titans Fan how are the Titans doing? 

Alexa, ask Titans Fan who do the Titans play next?

Alexa, ask Titans Fan Marcus Mariota (or any player's First name, Last name) touchdown update. 



Fun Facts about the Titans:


Alexa, ask Titans Fan to tell me some trivia about the Titans. 

Alexa, ask Titans Fan how many Super Bowls have the Titans won?
